<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="EN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Authentication Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f7fafd;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .header-box {
      background: #2d8cf0;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 24px 0;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fff;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(45,140,240,0.08);
      padding: 32px 28px 24px 28px;
    }
    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #222;
    }
    .code {
      color: #2d8cf0;
      background: #f0f7ff;
      padding: 16px 0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    p {
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header-box">Climb</div>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello, <%= display %>!</h2>
    <p>We received a request to <%=reason%></p>
    <p>Your authentication code is:</p>
    <div class="code"><%= code %></div>
    <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email. Please use this code to complete your authentication process.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>